final_mermaid_code:
graph TB
    subgraph Process
        StartEvent([Notice received by phone])
        Notice[Notice]
        AnswerNotice[Answer notice]
        RecordNotice[Record notice]
        StorePrintNotice[Store and print notice]
        XOR1{{Patient is known?}}
        CreatePatientFile[Create patient file]
        CloseCase[Close case]
        Timer1([Wednesday morning])
        AssignIntakers[Assign intakers]
        StoreAssignment[Store assignment]
        Parallel1{{ParallelGateway}}
        HandOutCards[Hand out cards]
        XOR2{{Medical file required?}}
        AskForMedicalFile[Ask for medical file]
        Timer2([Medical file received])
        UpdatePatientFile[Update patient file]
        Parallel2{{ParallelGateway}}
        PlanMeetingFirstIntaker[Plan meeting first intaker]
        MeetingDate1([Meeting date (1st intaker)])
        MeetFirstIntaker[Meet with first intaker]
        CompleteFile1[Complete file with 1st information]
        PlanMeetingSecondIntaker[Plan meeting second intaker]
        MeetingDate2([Meeting date (2nd intaker)])
        MeetSecondIntaker[Meet with second intaker]
        TypeOutConversation[Type out conversation]
        CompleteFile2[Complete file with 2nd information]
        Timer3([Wednesday morning 2])
        DetermineTreatment[Determine treatment]
        EndEvent([intake completed])
    end

    StartEvent --> AnswerNotice
    Notice -.-> AnswerNotice
    AnswerNotice --> RecordNotice
    RecordNotice --> StorePrintNotice
    StorePrintNotice --> XOR1
    XOR1 -->|Patient is unknown| CreatePatientFile
    XOR1 -->|Patient is known| CloseCase
    CreatePatientFile --> CloseCase
    CloseCase --> Timer1
    Timer1 --> AssignIntakers
    AssignIntakers --> StoreAssignment
    StoreAssignment --> Parallel1
    Parallel1 --> HandOutCards
    Parallel1 --> XOR2
    XOR2 -->|Medical file required| AskForMedicalFile
    XOR2 -->|Medical file not required| PlanMeetingFirstIntaker
    AskForMedicalFile --> Timer2
    Timer2 --> UpdatePatientFile
    UpdatePatientFile --> Parallel2
    Parallel2 --> PlanMeetingFirstIntaker
    Parallel2 --> PlanMeetingSecondIntaker
    PlanMeetingFirstIntaker --> MeetingDate1
    MeetingDate1 --> MeetFirstIntaker
    MeetFirstIntaker --> CompleteFile1
    PlanMeetingSecondIntaker --> MeetingDate2
    MeetingDate2 --> MeetSecondIntaker
    MeetSecondIntaker --> TypeOutConversation
    TypeOutConversation --> CompleteFile2
    CompleteFile1 --> Timer3
    CompleteFile2 --> Timer3
    Timer3 --> DetermineTreatment
    DetermineTreatment --> EndEvent
